%OPTION  ===>_ZCMD

%                      'AUTO'   primary command
+                      ------------------------

   Primary command%AUTO+allows you enable or disable Reasm automatic act
   The format of AUTO command is:

  %A{UTO} ON/OFF+

   AUTO OFF is useful in case you feel REASM is 'too smart' and you pref
have the full manual control on all the project changes.


   Examples:
  %AUTO    OFF+- Disable auto actions
  %A        ON+- Enable  auto actions

